---
title: Middle Eastern Roast Veggie Pilaf Rice with Almonds, Feta & Garlic Yoghurt
description: We wanted to give you a big hug today, so we hope this roast veggie pilaf rice will suffice. It’s fluffy and packed
full of hearty veggies we know you love like chermoula pumpkin. The creamy feta sprinkled on top is our way of
showing just how much we love you.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
